data.description: Gorgeous Lennar home located in Mountaingate. Seller is willing to credit buyer $5000 for closing cost or allowance for paint. This beauty features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. As you unlock the door there is an office to the left that can be used as office or bedroom. If you love to entertain this floor plan is perfect. Your great room is perfect for family gatherings. The kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedrooms features a separate tub and shower. The backyard is a plus. The large covered patio is perfect for those summer bbqs. If your tired of small yards then this one you will LOVE and you also get Rv parking.
